Class HLCA

    Vocabulary definitions for HLCA in Mining Minds v2.0. Concepts of the Context Ontology which represents the Mining Minds Context Model.

      • unidentifiedHlc

        public static final java.lang.String unidentifiedHlc
        Name used to represent the Unidentified PhysicalActivity and Nutrition Context. Please note that this concept is only used by the HLC Notifier but it is not part of the Context Ontology. This is done in this way in order to ensure the Context Ontology extensibility.
